  "title": "ISic003009. Dedication to Damater(?)",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Δάματρι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δάματρι\"><span data-text=\"Δάματρι\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">Δάμ̣[ατρι]</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">[καὶ]</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κόραι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κόραι\"><span data-text=\"Κόραι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">[Κόραι]</span></span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"βασιλ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">βασιλ</span>  <span data-text=\"έα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">[έα]</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\n                    βασι λέος Γέλωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\"><span data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">[Ἱερώνυμον]</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"βασι\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">βασι</span>  <span data-text=\"λέος\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">[λέος]</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γέλωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Γέλωνος\"><span data-text=\"Γέλωνος\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">[Γέλωνος]</span></span></span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Συρακόσιοι\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"\">[Συρακόσιοι]</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Δάματρι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δάματρι\"><span data-text=\"Δάματρι\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">ΔΑ.[....</span></span></span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">...</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κόραι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κόραι\"><span data-text=\"Κόραι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">.....]</span></span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"βασιλ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">ΒΑΣΙΛ</span><span data-text=\"έα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">[..</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\n                    βασι λέος Γέλωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\"><span data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">.........]</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"βασι\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">ΒΑΣΙ</span><span data-text=\"λέος\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">[....</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γέλωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Γέλωνος\"><span data-text=\"Γέλωνος\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">.......]</span></span></span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Συρακόσιοι\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"\">[..........]</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003009_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 2018\" src=\"ISic003009_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003009.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 2018\" src=\"ISic003009-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003009_scale_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 2021-10-06\" src=\"ISic003009_scale_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003009_scale.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 2021-10-06\" src=\"ISic003009_scale-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003009_left_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 2021-10-06\" src=\"ISic003009_left_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003009_left.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 2021-10-06\" src=\"ISic003009_left-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003009_top_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 2021-10-06\" src=\"ISic003009_top_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003009_top.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag 2021-10-06\" src=\"ISic003009_top-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Manganaro 1977, checked against stone</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>The Syracusans dedicate (this statue of) King Hieronymos, son of King Gelon, to Damater and Kore</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The text is speculatively restored in several different ways by previous editors: the text of Manganaro 1977 is provided here as an example; Gentili 1961 instead suggested a dedication to Demeter and Kore by Gelon, son of Hieron. Manganaro is correct that there is theoretically space for a shorter fourth line, and the dedication to Zeus Hellanios in honour of Gelon (<a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003331\" target=\"_blank\">ISic003331</a> provides a plausible parallel.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 56.1103.2.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 34.0979 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Gentili 1959-1960 19-20 fig.2 </li><li> Gentili 1961 8-10 no.3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001955\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001955</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1963 24 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001848\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001848</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1965 186 no.2 tav.64 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1965 315 n.11 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001840\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001840</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1977 155-156 dr ph </li><li> Dimartino 2006 no.2.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002022\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002022</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Thinly incised broad letters of regular height, without serifs or marked terminations to the strokes. Alpha has straight bar; Beta has closed loops, in the second instance separated from one another. Sigma has parallel top and bottom strokes, the mid-strokes meeting slightly over halfway across.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Β-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Β type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Β-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Β type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ι type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Σ-tyoe3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Σ tyoe3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Σ-type3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Σ type3</a> </p> Line 1-3  60  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not measured  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
