tion-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Δάματρι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δάματρι\"><span data-text=\"Δάματρι\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">ΔΑ.[....</span></span></span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">...</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κόραι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κόραι\"><span data-text=\"Κόραι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">.....]</span></span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"βασιλ\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">ΒΑΣΙΛ</span><span data-text=\"έα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"\">[..</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\n                    βασι λέος Γέλωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\"><span data-text=\"Ἱερώνυμον\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"\">.........]</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"βασι\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"\">ΒΑΣΙ</span><span data-text=\"λέος\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"\">[....</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γέλωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Γέλωνος\"><span data-text=\"Γέλωνος\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"\">.......]</span></span></span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"Συρακόσιοι\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"\">[..........]</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
