      "id": "translation",
      "html": "<h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>The Syracusans dedicate (this statue of) King Hieronymos, son of King Gelon, to Damater and Kore</p>  "
